 WILLY IN THE CASTLE OF DREAMS CODES :
 -------------------------------------
 1:------  2:GLUB  3:TRIFF  4:FRUIT  5:XYZZY  6:FLUSH  7:HIFI  8:FLASH
 9:XENON  10:JOHN  11:LENIN  12:TURBO  13:BOOZE  14: ZEFF  15:OMEGA
 16:TBEAR  17:AHB  18: SHARK  19:PUMPY  20:DROBB  21:KIMMY


 SENSIBLE SOCCER :
 -----------------
 TO SCORE A GOAL EVERY TIME, KICK THE BALL TOWARDS THE GOALIE.  WHEN A
 FORWARD GETS THE BALL KICK IT ACROSS THE GOAL MOUTH AND USE THE AFTER
 TOUCH TO BEND IT INTO THE NET

 
 PARASOL STARS :
 ---------------

 TPYE :->CYNIX<- DURING THE GAME THEN YOU CAN USE THE FOLLOWING KEYS.

 M - GET ALL 3 STARS      G - KILL ALL BADDIES ON SCREEN
 C - EXTRA CREDIT         D - DIE (USEFUL)
 X - SKIP TO EXTRA LEVEL  T - END THE STAGE
 1-7 - SKIP STAGES        F1-F10 - SKIP LEVELS
             B - SKIP TO BONUS SCREEN


 JAGUAR XJ-220 :
 ---------------

 SELECT SOUND EFFECTS AND THEN MODE. THEN TUNE THE RADIO INTO 64.5(THE MUSIX
 OF THE A-TEAM).   ANOTHER TIP IS SOON AS YOU HEAR 'GO' PRESS FIRE AND FORWARD
 ON THE JOYSTICK AND YOU WILL WIN THE RACE.


 THE MANAGER :
 -------------

 SELECT 2 MANAGER GAME THEN LET 1 PLAYER PUT A PLAYER ON THE MARKET, AND LET
 THE SECOND PLAYER MAKE AN OFFER FOR THE PLAYER MAKE PLAYER 1 REJECT THE OFFER
 AND WITHDRAW HIM FROM THE TRANSFER MARKET AND NOW HE WILL HAVE SCORED 99
 GOALS AND YOU WILL RECEIVE £75.000 AT THE END OF THE SEASON.

 SOON AS THE GAME STARTS GOTO THE PREFRENCES THEN PLACE THE CURSOR OVER THE 
 MAIN MENU ARROW THEN PRESS ~D~ THEN ~A~ NOW YOU WILL HAVE £24.999.999 AND
 ALL YOUR PLAYERS WILL HAVE 99% EVERYTHING (DO THIS AS MUCH AS U LIKE).


 ADDAMS FAMILY CODES :
 ---------------------

 L1191 - EXTRA ENERGY
 61H1C - RESCUE PUGSLEY
 B&198 - RESCUE GRANNY
 B?KKV - RESCUE FESTER
 BLS1T - RESCUE WEDNESDAY

 
 NICK FALDO'S CHAMPIONSHIP GOLF :
 --------------------------------

 ON THE TITLE SCREEN TYPE:->MAJORTOM<- TO PLAY A SPECIAL 9 HOLE COURSE ON MARS


 ROBOCOD :
 ---------

 TYPE IN :->LITTLE M<- TO BRING UP A LEVEL SELECT SCREEN BETWEEN 1 & 50
 
 WALK RIGHT TO THE FIRST SANTA'S SIGN AND EXTEND TO LOOK ABOVE COLLECT THE
 ITEMS IN THIS ORDER   CAKE, HAMMER, EARTH, APPLE, TAP FOR THE CHEAT.


 BODY BLOWS :
 ------------

 ON THE TITLE SCREEN  PRESS AND HOLD LEFT ON JOYSTICK IN PORT 2, PRESS AND 
 HOLD RIGHT ON JOYSTICK IN PORT 1 FOR 6 SECONDS FOR THE CHEAT MENU.


 APIDYA :
 --------

 TYPE IN ON THE TITLE SCREEN :

 SHOWCREDITS (PLUS RETURN) - FOR END SEQUENCE
 MISSHONEYBEE
 DEPUTYOFLOVE
 SNEAKPREVIEW


 SPACE CRUSADE (AND DATA DISK) :
 -------------------------------

 WHEN YOU'RE BEING ATTACKED PRESS THE ESC KEY A FEW TIMES TO REDUCE YOUR
 ATTACKERS SCORE.


 COVER GIRL POKER :
 ------------------

 TYPE AT ANY TIME :->DANCEOFTHESEVENDEVILS<-.  



 MAD BOMBER :
 ------------
 
 PRESS F5 ON THE TITLE SCREEN TO START OF LEVEL 13.

 
 THE COOL CROC TWINS :
 ---------------------

 LEVEL CODES : TRIAX,  DREAM,  MUNGO, JANKO, HENRI,  DOORS,  FLOYD, BRUNO
               MONEY,  HUMAN,  GIRLS.


 TOP SECRET :
 ------------

 PRESS F10 TO SKIP TO THE NEXT LEVEL.

 
 RISKY WOODS :
 -------------

 TRY PRESSING :

 F1 - MORE ENERGY
 F2 - MORE CASH
 F3 - SKIP STAGE

 
 HOOK :
 ------

 GO TO THE BAIT & TACKLE PICK UP THE MUG NEXT TO THE CANDLE THEN KEEP DOING 
 PICK UP WHERE THE MUG USED TO BE TO GET ALL THE OBJECTS YOU REQUIRE.


 MIGHT & MAGIC III :
 -------------------

 TELEPORTER CODES ARE : 

 HOME,  SEADOG,  FREEMAN,  DOOMED,  REDHOT,  AIR,  WATER,  FIRE,  EARTH.


 FIRE AND ICE :
 --------------

 WHEN PLAYING TYPE IN :->COOL<-.


 PREMIERE :
 ----------

 ON THE TITLE SCREEN TYPE :->SPARKPLUGS<- FOR THE CHEAT SCREEN.


 ZOOL :
 ------

 TYPE IN :->GOLDFISH<- ON THE TITLE SCREEN THEN PRESS F1-F6 TO SKIP LEVELS :
 
 IN GAME KEYS :->
 F1-F6 - SKIP LEVELS      1 - INVINSIBLE (SHEILD)
 2 - SKIP TO NEXT LEVEL   3 - JUMP A WHOLE LEVEL (EG. 1.3 THEN 2.3)
 4 - KILL YURSELF (FUCK THIS AGAIN SADISTIC PROGRAMMERS).


