 AGONY :
 -------
 
 WHEN GAME SAYS PRESS FIRE TO PLAY TYPE :->FANTASY<- THEN PRESS :

 F1 - FOR SWORDS      F3 - EXTRA POINTS/WEAPONS     F4 - EXTRA LIVES


 PINBALL FANTASIES :
 -------------------

 TYPE ->EXTRA BALLS<- FOR 5 BALLS OR TYPE ->DIGITIAL ILLUSIONS<- SO YOU CAN
 NOT LOSE THE BALL.


 ASSASSIN :
 ----------

 TYPE YOUR NAME ON THE HIGH SCORE TABLE AS ->MIDAN<- TO RESTART THE LEVEL
 YOU LAST DIED ON.


 ROAD RASH :
 -----------

 ENTER THE CODE :

 21132 O11H7
 VUKBE 27QAG

 TO START LEVEL 2 WITH THE DIABLO 1000 AND £41.000.000.


 LETHAL WEAPON :
 ---------------

 MISSION 1 - KSIIFL
 MISSION 2 - ECYOIR 
 MISSION 3 - FLRSKB
 MISSION 4 - UEOASF

 PRESS THE RELEVANT KEY FOR EACH CHEAT :

 ALT - Y - I = TURN OFF SPRITE COLLISIONS
 ALT - Y - K = INCREASE AMMO
 ALT - Y - L = INCREASE LIVES 
 ALT - Y - M = REMOVE SPRITES AND PLATFORMS 
 ALT - Y - N = CORRECT SPRITES AND PLATFORMS
 ALT - Y - Q = GAME COMPLETION CREDITS
 ALY - Y - 1-0 = SKIP TO REVELANT STAGE


 ATOM SMASHER :
 --------------

 TYPE ->CATHERINE ZETA JONES<- ON THE TITLE SCREEN. THEN IN GAME PRESS `I'
 TO BECOME INVINCIBLE.


 PREMIER MANAGER :  
 -----------------

 WHEN ON TELEPHONE DIAL 753423, 250967, 000123, 220769, 781560.


